Reclusa::

She smiled at this. She was actually rather pleased that Hydras had
seen her value. Despite her inner programs, she was starting to
actually admire him. Perhaps it was his leadership skills, or his aura
of power that he possessed. But even in her self centered and almost
empty spark, she felt a small micron of liking to him. 
"I would be honored."
